  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-note conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"9843c0b0-339d-4fef-a2d4-7a03e27494e7\" data-macro-name=\"note\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-warning confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><p>In the parameters below, some of them can be overridden by a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542217837/PxrLayer\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayer</a> when connected to the <strong>Input Material </strong>or through a <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542218974/PxrLayerMixer\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayerMixer</a>. <a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542216714/PxrLayerSurface\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrLayerSurface</a> is designed to better illustrate which parameters are not able to be overridden in a layer by including only parameters that are global. We recommend this material when you know you will be layering. The results of these settings are unchanged.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Bold Face</strong> parameters are layerable, able to be overridden per layer.</p></li><li><p><em>Italicized</em> parameters are not able to be layered or overridden. These are globally obeyed for all layers. For example: Choosing GGX as a specular model will mean all layers will be GGX for that parameter.</p></li></ul></div></div><p><span class=\"confluence-anchor-link conf-macro output-inline\" data-hasbody=\"false\" data-local-id=\"51828171-5364-4775-8bde-1145205ea479\" data-macro-id=\"093116c2-dae7-43a5-a64f-ad28a0bbef40\" data-macro-name=\"anchor\" id=\"FuzzParameters-top\"><span class=\"confluence-anchor-link\" id=\"top\"> </span></span></p><h3 id=\"FuzzParameters-FuzzParameters\">Fuzz Parameters</h3><p>This parameter introduces a bit of retroreflection and helps simulate fabrics, fuzz, and fine powder.</p><p><strong>Gain</strong></p><p>Fuzz weight. Higher numbers increase this effect. Below the <strong>Cone Angle</strong> is set to 16.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216093\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain0.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"e399e5d8-83b8-4d6d-92b7-15daad09f236\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain0.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216096\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain05.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"482682a3-b5e7-4d83-859b-1a25b9ebf8eb\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain05.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216099\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain10.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f073f9ba-f073-4eff-926d-3422d73bb1f0\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzGain10.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502353&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><p><strong>Color</strong></p><p>Fuzz color. This simulates a soft velvety-like effect. This is applied &quot;on top&quot; of the previous Specular lobes and may resemble dirt or fine dust. Below the <strong>Cone Angle</strong> is set to 16.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216102\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"f9104913-f2bf-4e66-807f-40fc52e99388\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502531&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216105\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor2.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3c763dd3-9f14-446f-b155-03cebb9d8c1b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor2.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216108\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor3.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"ac4664bb-47af-447e-9d5f-cc1059b8c52e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzColor3.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502532&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><p><strong>Cone Angle</strong></p><p>Fuzz roughness (corresponding to Marschner R cone angle). Note that we use something from Marschner's hair model here. This helps to simulate a similar response to hair/fur. Higher numbers increase the effect at facing angles. Below are values 8, 16, and 20.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216090\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle8.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"6740686e-db53-40f7-a34d-6f15d2f63850\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle8.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle16.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle16.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216087\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle16.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"18f46cf7-aa89-4c9a-bc6c-614846377262\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle16.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle16.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle32.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle32.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216084\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle32.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1b8bcc81-4af8-41f3-950f-53d9d0a825e7\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle32.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_coneAngle32.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502119&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><p><strong>Bump</strong></p><p>Normal to use for the fuzz illumination. If this is not set, it will use the global bump normal specified in the Properties near the bottom of this page.</p><p><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"463\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzBump1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502726&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzBump1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502726&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"384\" data-width=\"384\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542216111\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rman_pxrsurf_fuzzBump1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542216066\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"c615fdf0-5d23-4d7b-9d31-e384c21aeb7c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542216066/rman_pxrsurf_fuzzBump1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330502726&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=384&amp;height=384 